    "However, at the same time some other literature states the opposite is true as some aspects of the modeled applications are general.",
    "An adequate policy gradient (a mapping from state to action) generalizes well; for example, turning on the heating when the indoor temperature is low remains the same for almost every building regardless of the other possible goals.",
